## ðŸ”¥ Features

- ðŸ”„ Fully synced zombies (across all clients)
- ðŸ§  Realistic zombie movement & animations
- ðŸ’¥ Audio immersion (HTML/NUI based)
- ðŸ§ª Configurable zombie loot system
- ðŸ” SafeZone support (no spawn)
- ðŸš« Full ambient control (no traffic, no random peds)
- âš™ï¸ Optimized and easy to configure

